#################################
SXDL - Simple Xml Document Layout
#################################

This should become a library after a little more development.

sxdl should be possible to render a language that is oriented
on HTML. This language is neither a subset of HTML nor will
there be huge capabilites.

I design it for replacing webkit in gosm. since the functionality
used in gosm is really marginal, this should not be too difficult.

For the moment, sxdl only supports the following tags:

### basic text
<font>some text here</font>

### line-breaks
<br />

### images
<img src="your image path" />

### tables
<table>
	<tr>
		<td>other tags here</td>
		...
	</tr>
	...
</table>

